help:
compact collection
warning: this operation has blocking behaviour and is slow. You can cancel with killOp()
{ compact : <collection_name>, [dryRun:<bool>], [force:<bool>], [freeSpaceTargetMB:<int64_t>] }
  dryRun - runs only the estimation phase of the compact operation
  force - allows to run on a replica set primary
  freeSpaceTargetMB - minimum amount of space recoverable for compaction to proceed
